    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri'; font-size: 11pt;}\n.html-preview .ConsPlusNonformat {font-family: 'Courier New'; font-size: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 44px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 76px}</style><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 321.33333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилаётган суднинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">судига</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 321.33333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Ариза берувчи: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.Ш</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 321.33333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Манзил:</span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#6}Ариза берувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 321.33333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#7}Ариза берувчининг телефон рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 321.33333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Манфаатдор шахс: </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#9}Манфаатдор шахснинг Ф.И.Ш</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 321.33333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Манзил: </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#10}Манфаатдор шахснинг манзили</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 321.33333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Манфаатдор шахснинг телефон рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">(Мол-мулкни (ашёни) эгасиз деб топиш тўғрисида)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#13}Ашё топилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> санасида мен томонимдан </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#14}Ашё топилган ҳудуд</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> ҳудудида қуйидаги эгасиз қолдирилиб кетилган ашё (нарсалар) топилди: </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#15}Эгасиз ашёнинг номи, фарқловчи белгилари ва хусусиятлари</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">.<span class=\"leading\"></span>Бу бўйича қуйидаги гувоҳларнинг кўрсатмалари мавжуд: </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#16}Гувоҳларнинг Ф.И.Ш ва яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Ашёнинг эгасини топиш учун мен қуйидаги чораларни кўрдим: </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#17} Ашёнинг эгаси бўлган шахсларни аниқлаш бўйича қилинган ҳаракатлар кўрсатилади</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">.<span class=\"leading\"></span>Ҳозиргача ашёнинг эгаси номаълум.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Ариза берувчининг кўрсатилган ашёга бўлган ҳуқуқларига эътироз билдирувчи бошқа шахслар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Юқоридагиларга кўра ҳамда Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 191-моддаси ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик процессуал кодексининг 293-моддасига асосан,</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">СЎРАЙМАН:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Юқорида номи келтирилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#15}Эгасиз ашёнинг номи, фарқловчи белгилари ва хусусиятлари</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> ашёни эгасиз деб топишни ва унга нисбатан мулк ҳуқуқига эгалигимни тан олишни.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Илова; </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#18}Илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар рўйхати</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.Ш</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#3}Ариза имзоланган сана</span></p>\n</div></div>",
